headline.main: Pending Home Sales Drop to 10-Month Low in November
headline.print_headline: Pending Home Sales Drop to 10-Month Low in November

docs.snippet: Contracts to buy previously owned U.S. homes fell in November to their lowest level in nearly a year, a sign rising interest rates could be weighing on the housing market, the National Association of Realtors said on Wednesday....
docs.lead_paragraph: Contracts to buy previously owned U.S. homes fell in November to their lowest level in nearly a year, a sign rising interest rates could be weighing on the housing market, the National Association of Realtors said on Wednesday.
